theorem groupoid.is_isomorphic_iff_nonempty_hom {C : Type u} [Groupoid.{v} C] {X Y : C} :
    IsIsomorphic X Y ↔ Nonempty («expr ⟶ » X Y) :=
  (Groupoid.isoEquivHom X Y).nonempty_congr
